         Output: _age_default_vle_function_start_var_55.id, _age_default_vle_function_start_var_55.properties
   ->  Custom Scan (AGE VLE Stream)
         Output: _age_default_alias_0.edges
         VLE Shape: terminal-vertex
         VLE Arguments: 8
         VLE Argument Slots: graph=const, start=dynamic, end=const, edge=const, lower=const, upper=const, direction=const, grammar-node=const
         VLE Graph: cypher_vle
         VLE Edge: label=, properties=0
         VLE Edge Source: global-metadata, fixed-source=out=none/in=none, candidates=age_adjacency=-/- endpoint-btree=-/-, state=global-edge-state
         VLE Endpoints: start=runtime-id, end=const-id
         VLE Range: 1..2
         VLE Direction: right
         VLE Output: terminal-vertex(requirement=terminal-vertex, grammar=terminal-only)
         VLE Materialization: terminal-vertex-container, object-source=global-metadata
(17 rows)

